You'll be released after the movie.

1197
01:19:23,620 --> 01:19:25,737
Yes, he did.

1198
01:19:26,540 --> 01:19:28,532
But I can't do this!

1199
01:19:28,700 --> 01:19:31,135
Are you afraid people will see
how evil you are?

1200
01:19:31,300 --> 01:19:32,814
I am not evil!

1201
01:19:33,100 --> 01:19:35,057
I am innocent.

1202
01:19:35,540 --> 01:19:37,497
Wanyan died because of me.

1203
01:19:38,340 --> 01:19:41,731
Have me shot, I deserve it.

1204
01:19:41,900 --> 01:19:46,179
But she shouldn't be humiliated.

1205
01:19:46,340 --> 01:19:48,252
She was a noble person.

1206
01:19:48,420 --> 01:19:51,731
- She had honour.
- So, what did you do...

1207
01:19:52,420 --> 01:19:55,777
- ...to cause her death that day?
- I can't tell you.

1208
01:19:55,940 --> 01:19:57,932
- Why?
- Because I don't remember!

1209
01:20:03,620 --> 01:20:07,011
She was very happy that day.

1210
01:20:07,220 --> 01:20:09,052
She asked me to say "I love you."

1211
01:20:09,380 --> 01:20:12,100
I didn't. She wanted me to marry her.

1212
01:20:13,460 --> 01:20:15,497
I wouldn't.

1213
