We're ruined.

1234
01:21:38,060 --> 01:21:39,972
Indeed.

1235
01:21:40,140 --> 01:21:43,577
- May I share a thought?
- Out with it!

1236
01:21:45,020 --> 01:21:47,137
Show a man's face...

1237
01:21:47,300 --> 01:21:49,940
...followed by a baby,
you see tenderness.

1238
01:21:50,100 --> 01:21:51,454
